merical results for $pp\\to(\\mathrm{jet}\\,h)X$ in\nthe new framework, and find excellent agreement with existing LHC experimental\ndata.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2016 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Nov 2016 21:00:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-29"}
